column17:
Paul Smith Floral Eau de Parfum - 100 ml (For Women) Price: Rs.2537

Welcome a new day smelling as fresh as a freshly cut bouquet of assorted flowers. Pamper your senses and make heads turn with this mesmerizing floral fragrance from Paul Smith. Launched in 2005 this exquisite Eau de Parfum is a unique formulation from perfumer Laurent Bruyere that recreates the mystical magic of flowery fragrances and captures the sensuous woman in you. This Paul Smith concoction bears a special summery feel and makes a perfect day wear for the self-aware and innately beautiful woman. The luscious aroma is a gorgeous and intensively researched combination of flower extracts and forms a perfect luxury wear for special occasions.

The first impression creates an amalgamation of the intense scents of Ginger Sweet Orange Pink Grapefruit and Water Lily while the heart of the fragrance lies in the fresh note of Osmanthus White Magnolia and Orchids. The base note for this Paul Smith luxury perfume lies in the harmonious essences of Exotic Woods Tonka Bean Amber and Musk that linger on to leave you feeling quintessentially feminine and elegant. An attractive packaging in a graceful delicate flask-like vial placed within a canned container presents an innovative and impressive choice for the contemporary urban woman for whom her perfume is an extension of her personal expressions and individuality.

column17:
Paul Smith Extreme Eau de Toilette - 100 ml (For Women) Price: Rs.2510

Since ages perfumes have been precious additions to a woman's sensuality. This plush fragrance from Paul Smith is a part of its Extreme Eau de Toilette collection and was designed by Perfumer Antoine Maisondieu as a complement to its masculine counterpart the Paul Smith Extreme Man. Designed in illustrous celebration of femininity this luxury perfume has an earthy floral feel that takes you closer to nature. With dominant woody and green accords this Paul Smith aroma rejuvenates with its scintillating scent and accentuates the seductive woman in you. The delightful spring-time illusion recreated by this mesmerizing fragrance owes itself to the essence of nature and natural ingredients. While the top note dictated by Black Currant Mandarin Orange Green Tea and Bergamot this Paul Smith Extreme perfume creates a distinctive first impression the heart note that follows encompasses the scents of Cassia Freesia and Lily of the Valley. The rich base note offers the aroma of Sandalwood Amber Patchouli Vetiver and Cedar. With a contemporary square glass bottle packaging this intense aromatic concoction from Paul Smith leaves a lingering effect on the spirit and mind and engages the body with a freshness of feeling.
